data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful 6 bedroom Home in Forestdale Park subdivision. Great curb appeal with a front porch and located in a cul de sac. Newer roof on the garage and new front door on the home. Bright and sunny living room features a wood burning fireplace, bay window, and high ceilings. Gleaming hardwood floors throughout the home. Eat in kitchen features many wood cabinets. Formal dining room with hardwood flooring. Main floor also has a full updated bathroom. 2 nice size bedrooms also located on the main level. Large primary bedroom has beautiful wood beams. The second floor features 4 bedrooms and a full hallway bath. Full unfinished basement has a half bath and lots of storage space. New hot water heater in 2021. Furnace and Central AC new in 2008. 2 car detached garage and beautiful brick paver patio in the backyard. See this Home soon! Property sold as-is.
